metadata.name: Day 7 - Trip
metadata.description:
Editions of 3/3 - a gamified collection, read rules bellow: 

Collect 3x Inktober Tokens and you will be able to receive a physical painting as a gift. You will be able to choose any painting from the collection that is not already taken.

--------------------------------------------------

About The Project:

Inktober is a yearly challenge that happens every October. On year 2022 I decided to go along the official prompt list, yet Instead of Ink I am using acrylic paint to create my artworks.
